videos.description: Steven Haney pulls up in transition and knocks down a deep 3-pointer.
videos.headline: LMU's Haney buries deep triple

videos.description: Corey Kispert extends the Gonzaga lead with a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Kispert knocks down a second chance 3-pointer

videos.description: Rui Hachimura gets the and-1 after going coast-to-coast for Gonzaga.
videos.headline: Hachimura goes coast-to-coast and finishes after taking contact

videos.description: Steven Haney keeps LMU close against Gonzaga with two 3-pointers on consecutive possessions.
videos.headline: Haney hits back-to-back 3-pointers for LMU

videos.description: Gonzaga's Johnathan Williams runs the pick-and-roll to perfection as he finishes with an easy slam.
videos.headline: Williams slams it off the pick and roll

videos.description: Gonzaga's Johnathan Williams cuts down the middle of the lane and finishes with an easy slam.
videos.headline: Williams makes it look easy with another slam

videos.description: Josh Perkins comes up with a clean block on Mattias Markusson starting a fast break.
videos.headline: Gonzaga point guard Perkins blocks LMU big man
